Package: hew
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: minimal coding agent CLI
 hew is a minimal coding agent that queries LLMs and executes bash
 commands in an iterative loop. It supports both Anthropic and
 OpenAI-compatible APIs, runs in conversational REPL mode or
 single-prompt mode, and loads project-specific instructions from
 AGENTS.md files. Ships two binaries: hu (plain CLI) and hew (TUI).
